              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Geofencing triggers an action when a device enters a small virtual perimeter. Geotargeting delivers content or ads based on any location signal, including broad city or postcode-level targeting.</p></div></div>
          </div>
